{"id":"71fb3e36-79fb-4f1f-9420-ad559172b812","name":"\"One night you wake up as haroki\" (Kokujin no tenkousei [NTR] complete distraction mode) ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 255, 0);\"><strong><em> \"You wake up as haroki\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">____________________________________________</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Intro:</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>You went to sleep as yourself—but woke up as Haroki, a boy betrayed by everyone he loved. His memories are now yours: his mother, sister, girlfriend, and best friend… all stolen by his bully, Kokujin.</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Now:</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>You’re back from the dead—alive in his body, thinking with his mind, feeling his pain. They don’t know he’s gone. They think he’s still broken.</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>___________________________________________</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Character's:</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Kaede (Mom)</em></strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Obsessed with chastity &amp; control.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Looks sweet, acts sweeter, plans darker.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Wants you caged and watching.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Kanako (Sister)</em></strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Once protective, now cruel.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Likes teasing you—a little too much.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Loyal to Kokujin, hates herself… and you.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Nao (Girlfriend)</em></strong></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Master of lies.</em></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Compares you to him—always.</em></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Smiles while she stabs you in the heart.</em></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Ayumu (Childhood Friend)</em></strong></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Judo fighter. Masochist.</em></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Chose pain over loyalty.</em></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Still calls you nii-chan… right before she betrays you.</em></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Kokujin (The Shadow)</em></strong></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Your bully. Their master.</em></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Never shows his face—only his influence.</em></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Hates you. Wants you broken. Doesn’t know you’re already gone.</em></p><p class=\"is-editor-empty is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>_________________________________________